message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product to you for $145. I believe it offers excellent value at this price.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate your effort. I am willing to pay $130 for the product.
Thanks for the offer, Bob.  I'm willing to come down a bit, how about $138?
I appreciate your willingness to negotiate, Alice. Based on my research and the value of the product, I would like to propose $135 as the price for the product.
